These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, fanta, juice, water
City: edinburgh, rome, hannover, boston
1. the person drinking fanta is the fan of techno##1
2. the person drinking juice is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person drinking fanta is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Beverage   | water | fanta | juice | mirinda |
| City     | boston  | edinburgh       | rome    | hannover     |

