.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
House: cottage, wooden, futuristic, craftsman
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, whist, scrabble
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, lacrosse, swimming, water-polo
1. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the craftsman house##1
2. the cottage house is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
4. the futuristic house is on the right of the wooden house##1
5. the person playing scrabble is between the owner of the frog and the person who's sport is ice-hockey##2
6. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the person playing scrabble and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person playing go is on the left of the futuristic house##1
9. the person playing whist is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| House         | craftsman | wooden    | futuristic  | cottage    |
| Game   | mah-jongg      | go  | scrabble  | whist |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Sport         | lacrosse    | water-polo | swimming | ice-hockey |

