.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
City: colone, miami, berlin, paris
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, fishing, photography, traveling
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, mauve, green, apricot
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person who likes green is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person who likes apricot##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
6. the person who likes mauve is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
7. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person traveling to colone is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who likes mauve##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| City        | miami | berlin     | colone   | paris     |
| Hobby       | fishing   | camping   | photography | traveling |
| Color         | black   | green | apricot       | mauve    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

