 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the wooden house##1
 6. the art-deco house is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person drinking coffee##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person drinking juice is between the victorian house and the person drinking sprite##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Beverage           | cola  | sprite | juice     | coffee |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| House           | wooden       | art-deco    | futuristic      | victorian           |
