.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
4 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla, guinea-pig, hamster
The people have 4 different jobs:  freelancer, lawyer, security-guard, social-worker
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, ebony, light-blue, purple
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, ice-hockey, sailing, weightlifting
 1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 2. the person who's sport is basketball is on the far left##1
 3. the security-guard is the owner of the chinchilla##1
 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
 5. the person who likes purple is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 6. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the person who likes purple##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 8. the lawyer is the person who likes ebony##1
 9. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who likes amber##2
10. the person who likes light-blue is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Pet          | chinchilla         | guinea-pig         | frog     | hamster      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
| Color   | amber      | light-blue       | purple    | ebony       |
| Sport         | basketball     | sailing       | weightlifting | ice-hockey |

