2. the freelancer is between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who growslily##2
3. the person who growsmarigold is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who growsrose##2
4. the librarian is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
5. the person who growsmarigold is the person who growsmarigold##1
6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person who's sport is cycling##1
7. the person who growsrose is on the left of the analyst##1
8. the person drinking lemonade is on the far right##1
9. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Job           | librarian | freelancer | analyst  | paramedic |
