 4. the person playing canasta is the person driving the train##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching zombie movies##1
 6. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the person drinking fanta is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
 9. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person drinking tea is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | fantasy | family  | zombie  |
| Game   | snooker       | canasta   | billiard | chess    |
