4. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the craftsman house##1
5. the person playing go is between the person playing backgammon and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the townhouse house is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the tower house is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
8. the farmhouse house is on the left of the craftsman house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
