 6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to paris and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
| City           | paris | san-francisco | liverpool   | prague |
